00:03:52,106 --> 00:03:53,441
Biar kuluruskan ini.

54
00:03:53,524 --> 00:03:57,362
Kau Du-sik, 
kau putri Paman Cheol-yong, dan…

55
00:03:58,279 --> 00:04:00,949
Dan kau bukan suami Du-sik 
yang menganggur,

56
00:04:01,032 --> 00:04:03,034
