kepada atasanku.

153
00:09:40,204 --> 00:09:42,290
Astaga, kau bukan hanya tampan.

154
00:09:42,373 --> 00:09:43,583
Apa?

155
00:09:43,666 --> 00:09:45,876
Kau juga baik hati. Itu tak adil!

156
00:09:46,502 --> 00:09:48,296
Soal itu, aku…

157
00:09:49,046 --> 00:09:51,549
Bagaimana jika kita berteman mulai kini?

158
00:09:52,049 --> 00:09:53,593
Setuju. Mari bicara kasual.

159
00:09:53,676 --> 00:09:55,928
- Aku juga, Seok-hui. 
- Bagus, Hyeon-uk.

160
00:09:56,012 --> 00:09:58,431
- Senang punya teman dari Seoul. 
- Benar.

161
00:09:59,015 --> 00:10:00,141
- Ayo lakukan ini. 
- Ya.

162
00:10:17,074 --> 00:10:18,826
Bola Salju, ayo makan kudapan.

163
00:10:19,869 --> 00:10:22,246
Apa itu tadi?

164
00:10:23,914 --> 00:10:24,790
Siapa itu?

165
00:10:31,088 --> 00:10:34,550
Kukira aku melihat seseorang. 
Mungkin hanya bayangan.

166
00:10:38,262 --> 00:10:39,347
Bola Salju.

167
00:10:39,889 --> 00:10:42,475
Jangan berkeliaran di luar hari ini.

168
00:10:42,975 --> 00:10:45,603
Tetaplah di rumah, ya?

169
00:10:46,187 --> 00:10:48,689
Atau polisi itu 
akan membuat keributan lagi.

170
00:10:50,358 --> 00:10:52,735
Kau tahu apa julukan Seok-hui?

171
00:10:53,444 --> 00:10:56,113
Julukannya "Bebal".

172
00:10:56,656 --> 00:11:00,826
Dia selalu bicara melantur, 
jadi, Geum-gang memberinya julukan itu.

173
00:11:00,910 --> 00:11:02,870
Apa pendapatmu? Cocok untuknya?

174
00:11:03,454 --> 00:11:05,748
Dia melakukannya lagi tadi.

175
00:11:05,831 --> 00:11:07,500
Maksudku, dia berpikir

176
00:11:07,583 --> 00:11:10,544
Bola Salju adalah saksi pembunuhan? 
Itu mustahil.

177
